text: WTUP-FM (99.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve Guntown, Mississippi, which serves Tupelo and northeast Mississippi with an ERP of 15,500 watts. WTUP-FM is owned by iHeartMedia.https://www.iheartmedia.com/iheartmedia/stations?city=Tupelo The station is the former WBIP-FM. ==References== ==External links== * TUP-FM Category:IHeartMedia radio stations
